        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer109857997" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9160775718154586844">What an journey. A Heart to Mend, by Myne Whitman proved to be an intriguing read, especially with that of the banking conflict. <br/><br/>I was intrigued not only with the main characters relationship, but with the location which the story takes place, Lagos, Africa. If you are a fan of love and redemption, this is a good read for you. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


