      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/10125389-a-heart-to-mend">Quotes from A Heart to Mend</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A lot of aspiring writers are actually very talented and just have to continue polishing their craft till opportunity knocks. <br /><br />All writers have to persevere, have a story they want to share and push till it's in a form others can understand and appreciate. <br /><br />To my fans and readers, I love you all and say a great big THANK YOU!&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/271132-a-lot-of-aspiring-writers-are-actually-very-talented-and">6 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;She didn’t believe there was anything like perfect, fairytale love. Most people were flawed and prone to mistakes. She thought herself a romantic but treated love with the same practicality she did most things. They’d had fall-outs and misunderstandings but she’d never been free to be herself like she was with Edward. She couldn’t imagine being with another person after him.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/271810-she-didn-t-believe-there-was-anything-like-perfect-fairytale-love">5 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
